# Demo vaults bundled as manual-test fixtures (not real secrets). The monorepo
# root .gitignore ignores *.kdbx to prevent committing real vaults; re-include
# these known-password demo vaults so the app's vault-open flow stays testable.
!fixtures/*.kdbx
